GZIP : 

    COMPRESS A FILE : gzip Filename

    DECOMPRESS A FILE : gunzip Filename


TAR ARCHIVES : 

    CREATE TAR ARCHIVE : tar cvf TarFilename.tar File_1 File_2 File_N

        CREATE : c
        VERBOSE : v
        FILENAME : f

    UNPACK ARCHIVES : tar xvf TarFilename.tar
        EXTRACT : x


INSTALL A PACKAGE : dpkg -i _package_name.deb

REMOVE A PACKAGE : dpkg -r _package_name.deb

LIST INSTALLED PACKAGES : dpkg -l


APT : 

    INSTALLATION : apt install package_name

    REMOVAL : apt remove package_name

    UPDATION : apt update;apt upgrade

    INSTALLED PACKAGE INFO : apt show package_name


OBSCURE PACKAGE OR PURE SOURCE CODE : 

    SOFTWARE TO INSTALL TOOLS TO ALLOW COMPILATION OF SOURCE CODE : sudo apt install build-essential

    EXTRACT CONTENTS : tar -xzvf package_name.tar.gz